Fumble
Discworld ritual help
Fumble

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
Fumble -- Makes the target drop their current weapon.
.EP

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
When fumble is perform upon a target, it causes them to become clumsy, dropping 
their current weapon. To perform this ritual, you need a holy symbol consecrated
to your God. Making someone fumble their weapon is an offensive act.
.EP
